  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EThis month\u0026rsquo;s webinar will review Pelvic, Abdominal, and Lumbar pain conditions and syndromes.\u0026nbsp; Some are very challenging to diagnose, and even tougher to treat.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EProtocols for clinical conditions seen in practice in an adaptive procedural format that will reveal that Low Level Laser therapy has much to offer these patients.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EJoin Dr. Chris Carraway as we delve into related topics, and ways to utilize Low Level Laser to help these patients.\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
